text: Paul Vermeiren is an archer from Belgium. Vermeiren competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics.Paul VERMEIREN He was born on 27 August 1963.Paul Vermeiren == References == Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian archers Category:Olympians for Belgium
